(2274, 1, '2015-09-01 00:37:33', '2015-09-01 00:37:33', 'For the moment we offer support only in ENGLISH!\n<h2 class="su-post-title" >\n    <a style="color: #f50d29; text-decoration:none"\n       onMouseOver="this.style.textDecoration=''underline''"\n       onMouseOut="this.style.textDecoration=''none''" href="http://localhost/bodrag/support/faqs/">F.A.Q.</a>\n</h2>\n<p>\nHere you will find answers to other users'' questions related to general problems like orders or downloads. Check here before contacting us!\n</p>\n<br>\n<h2 class="su-post-title">\n    <a style="color: #f50d29; text-decoration:none"\n       onMouseOver="this.style.textDecoration=''underline''"\n       onMouseOut="this.style.textDecoration=''none''" href="http://localhost/bodrag/support/tutorials/">Tutorials</a>\n</h2>\n<p>\nHere you will find some useful tutorials for our software products.\n</p>\n<br>\n<h2 class="su-post-title">\n    <a style="color: #f50d29; text-decoration:none"\n       onMouseOver="this.style.textDecoration=''underline''"\n       onMouseOut="this.style.textDecoration=''none''" href="http://localhost/bodrag/support/beta-testing/">Beta testing</a></h2>\n<p>\nJoin our beta testing program and help us improve our products. At the end of the testing process you will receive a free license key for the software you tested.\n</p>', 'Support', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'support', '', '', '2015-09-01 00:37:33', '2015-09-01 00:37:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bodrag/?page_id=2274', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(2279, 1, '2015-09-01 00:50:47', '2015-09-01 00:50:47', '[row]\n\n[span12]\n<p style="color:#b7b7b7; font-size:35px;  font-weight:bold;">Beta testing</p>\n[hr]\n[/span12]\n\n[/row]\n\nThank you for your interest in beta testing Bodrag products!\n\n<strong>What does a beta version really stands for?</strong>\n\nA beta product is an officially released version of a product which includes most of the product''s functionality. The beta version is released only for external testing of the product in order to identify various problems that may occur, as well as collect requirements and suggestions from possible clients or users.\n\nEach beta release includes a release notes file which provides the following information:\n• the release version number,\n• the list of improvements and modifications since the previous version ,\n• descriptions of known bugs (if any) and other relevant information,\n• system requirements for the testing computer.\n\nPlease note that a software beta version is <strong>NOT</strong> the final version, and the developer does not guarantee the product as errors-free. The tested product may disrupt the computer''s operation and/or result in data loss.\n\n<strong>What should a beta tester do?</strong>\n\n• You need to finish testing the product within one week after you receive it.\n• You must report all problems you experienced with the product. We also are interested in any suggestions you may have in order to improve this Bodrag product.\n• You may not discuss the content of the beta software with any third party unless specifically authorized by Bodrag.\n\n<strong>How can I become a beta tester?</strong>\n\nTo become a beta tester, you should:\n• Read the <a class="textlink" href="http://www.bodrag.com/page/beta_testing_agreement/">beta test agreement</a> carefully and accept it.\n\nAt the end of the testing process you will receive a free license key for the tested software.\n\nWe will analyze the survey including your suggestions and notify you if you are approved for the Bodrag beta testing program. Additional instructions on how to download the beta release software and report the results of your testing will be included in the notification e-mail.', 'Beta testing', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'beta-testing', '', '', '2015-09-01 00:50:47', '2015-09-01 00:50:47', '', 2274, 'http://localhost/bodrag/?page_id=2279', 0, 'page', '', 0),
