(2373, 1, '2015-09-02 17:23:50', '2015-09-02 17:23:50', '<strong>Nashua, NH</strong><strong> - </strong>Bodrag Software announced today the availability of Bodrag Utilities, the latest version of its PC optimization software previously based on a history of award winning optimization components.\n&nbsp;\nBodrag Utilities provides Windows users with a complete suite of optimization and maintenance software tools to ensure their computers remain reliable and fast. Bodrag Utilities supports Windows XP,Windows Vista &amp; Windows 7 (32-bit versions).\n&nbsp;\n<a title="Bodrag" href="http://localhost/bodrag/downloads/bodrag-utilities">Bodrag Utilities</a> enables users to optimize their PC so that little amount of effort and no extensive technical expertise are required. The develop team has focused on making it possible for users to optimize PCs with minimal effort, while maintaining complete control over any system. Based on the analysis of the PC and the user''s choices, Bodrag Utilities suggest only those measures that are safe for the system. It is also able to handle faulty configurations caused by other tools or applications.\n&nbsp;\n<strong><a>Bodrag Utilities Features:</a></strong>\n&nbsp;\n<strong>Optimizing</strong>\nBodrag Utilities optimizes the entire system, including memory and Internet connection. It also handles registry and hard disks defrag.\n&nbsp;\n<strong>Cleaning</strong>\nBodrag Utilities cleans disks available within the system, registry, securely shreds files and folders based on the most reliable methods available. On top of these it securely erases hard disks free space to make sure that old deleted documents are impossible to be recovered.\n&nbsp;\n<strong>Protecting</strong>\nBodrag Utilities monitors all applications at start-up and lets you know about possible sneaky ones.\nIt protects your online privacy based on Bodrag`s previous successful Wipe Expert application and also password protects your executables in order to prevent faulty use. It prevents installation of spyware to make sure your PC behaviour is not watched and also creates registry backups in order for you to maintain a stable system.\n&nbsp;\n<strong>Fixing and repairing</strong>\nBodrag Utilities manages:\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>your list of running applications</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>your list of start-up applications</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>your list of Windows services</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>uninstalling of your applications</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<strong>More Features: </strong>\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>Bodrag Utilities provides advanced details about your system and hardware</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>It helps customize your Windows interface and settings, helps change the desktop background</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>It is also able to schedule events like shut downs, sleep, and hibernate status</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<strong>Supported Windows versions</strong>\nThe software supports Windows XP and Windows Vista and Windows 7 (32-bit versions).\n&nbsp;\n<strong>Price and availability</strong>\nBodrag Utilities can be purchased for $44.95 via download at <a href="http://localhost/bodrag/downloads/bodrag-utilities">www.bodrag.com</a>\n&nbsp;\n<strong>About Bodrag </strong>\n<strong>Bodrag</strong> is a dynamic IT company with 100% U.S.A capital. It was established in 2004, in Nashua, NH. <strong>Bodrag</strong> was founded as a software development company. Bodrag is known for its award winning Windows products: Outlook Express Backup Expert, Wipe Expert, Foxmail Backup Expert and, the latest addition to the product portfolio, a RAM Booster Expert.\n', 'Bodrag Software Delivers Complete, Fast and Easy PC Optimization with Bodrag Utilities', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bodrag-software-delivers-complete-fast-and-easy-pc-optimization-with-bodrag-utilities', '', '', '2015-09-02 17:23:50', '2015-09-02 17:23:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bodrag/?p=2373', 0, 'post', '', 0),
